
			     GStreamer::Interfaces
			    -----------------------

GStreamer::Interfaces provides access to some of the interfaces in the
GStreamer Interfaces library.  Currently, that's only GStreamer::PropertyProbe.

				 Installation
				--------------

To install GStreamer, run the following commands:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

				 Dependencies
				--------------

GStreamer::GConf depends on any release of the 0.8 series of the GStreamer
Interfaces library and on the following Perl modules:

  ExtUtils::Depends
  ExtUtils::PkgConfig
  GStreamer >= 0.02
